data.description: Get ready to be amazed by this gem nestled in the picturesque golf course and lake community of Rancho El Dorado. This residence is more than just a home; it's a lifestyle! Immerse yourself in an incredible community with delightful children's playgrounds and scenic walking paths. This ideal split floorplan home boasts 3 bedrooms plus a den, complete with a charming built-in oak desk.  Your primary bedroom boasts a spacious walk-in closet and ensuite bathroom. Your luxurious soaking tub is perfectly situated underneath a stunning window to allow ample natural light. A top-notch security system will keep you feeling safe. But that's not all! This property has been recently updated with NEW carpet, NEW appliances, NEW ceiling fans throughout and luscious NEW green turf in your backyard!
